===================================================================
--- 
+++ 
@@ -0,0 +1,39 @@
+import { Column, Entity, Index, PrimaryGeneratedColumn } from "typeorm";
+
+export enum OperationType {
+    INIT = "init",
+    ACTUALIZE = "actualize",
+    BUY = "buy",
+    SELL = "sell",
+    BUY_FEE = "buy_fee",
+    SELL_FEE = "sell_fee"
+}
+
+@Entity()
+export class BalanceLog {
+    @PrimaryGeneratedColumn()
+    id: number;
+
+    @Index()
+    @Column({type: "int"})
+    accountId: number;    
+
+    @Index()
+    @Column({type: "int"})
+    balanceId: number;    
+    
+    
+    @Index()
+    @Column({
+        type: "enum",
+        enum: OperationType   
+    })
+    operationType: OperationType 
+
+    @Column("decimal")
+    amount: number;
+
+    @Column("decimal")
+    total: number;
+
+}
